x4freetext: The targets of isotopically pure Ti-48 and Ti-50 were
used.

x4freetext: Six surface barrier detectors were used.
0.5 to 5 mu-g/cm2 thick layers of 48Ti on 20 mu-g/cm2
thick carbon backings were used as targets.
